feedCard.headLines: Elon Musk reacts as Indian-American CEO hired woman to slap him every time he uses Facebook
feedCard.highLights: The CEO of the wearable device brand, Pavlok, Maneesh Sethi used to get distracted by Facebook during his work hours. He wished to enhance his business by working more and giving more time to his company instead of social media.
